name: Party Standee: "Raring to Go"
description: A dancer standee that serves as a symbol of the "Dance Dance Dynamic Disco" dance exchange event jointly organized by Natlan's People of the Springs, Flower-Feather Clan, and Children of Echoes in partnership with the Sumeru Eremites' Blazing Beasts. The standee itself is an excellent representation of a joyful Mualani mid-dance.\nEven the most seasoned of Sumeru dancers has something to learn from Mualani's moves, discovering fresh ideas and unlocking new avenues for dynamic expressions of joy.\nAvid dancers exploring new dance moves and uncovering unexpected expression in seemingly simple movements is precisely the reason the organizers are so passionate about this event.
